d\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1071, \"end\": 1074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.261374786097208e-17, \"text\": \"Iga\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\"}, {\"begin\": 1086, \"end\": 1092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999993932785423, \"rank\": 6.058178043879063e-07, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1155, \"end\": 1162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.99378948619804, \"rank\": 0.006248127996538132, \"text\": \"Romania\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irina-Camelia_Begu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irina-Camelia Begu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irina-Camelia_Begu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irina-Camelia_Begu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the day's headline act was always going to be the opening chapter of the 'Nadalcaraz' story which will surely etch itself into the Parisian red clay over the coming days.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the first time 14-time French Open champion Nadal and Alcaraz, winner of four Grand Slams including this year's French Open and Wimbledon, had played together in competition.\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7751022731812915e-26, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 1423, \"end\": 1430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2982258746175457e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were some misfires and Alcaraz admitted he was nervous playing with his idol, but they gelled quickly enough to subdue the skillful south American duo in front of Nadal's son Rafa Jr and the two daughters of Spain's King Felipe.\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1574, \"end\": 1581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2982258746175457e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 1689, \"end\": 1697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997812856858468, \"rank\": 0.00021868865579360112, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1714, \"end\": 1719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7751022731812915e-26, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 1726, \"end\": 1730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\", \"score\": 0.9999999810538613, \"rank\": 1.8946002870780615e-08, \"text\": \"Rafa\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\"}, {\"begin\": 1759, \"end\": 1764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999090505, \"rank\": 9.098099214762852e-11, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1767, \"end\": 1771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_of_Romania\", \"score\": 0.8696746990256004, \"rank\": 0.1453280927250735, \"text\": \"King\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_of_Romania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_of_Romania\"}, {\"begin\": 1772, \"end\": 1778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felipe_VI\", \"score\": 0.9999999871238289, \"rank\": 1.2876013414842917e-08, \"text\": \"Felipe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felipe_VI\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felipe_VI\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"An unforgettable moment for me, without a doubt,\\\" Nadal told reporters.\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1832, \"end\": 1837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7751022731812915e-26, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think for him too, to come out here on this stage and play together representing Spain in the Olympic Games is a combination that is difficult to beat.\\\"\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 2009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1938, \"end\": 1943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999090505, \"rank\": 9.098099214762852e-11, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal's preparation was unusual in the extreme, the Spaniard having spent Friday night carrying the Olympic torch in a boat on a choppy River Seine in the rain at the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2011, \"end\": 2016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7751022731812915e-26, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 2063, \"end\": 2071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.967418895808315, \"rank\": 0.03367836756036045, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}, {\"begin\": 2147, \"end\": 2158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were also injury concerns ahead of what is likely to be his last dance at Roland Garros, but Nadal rolled back the years on the rectangle of red dirt he first conquered when Alcaraz was a two-year-old.\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2277, \"end\": 2290, \"title\": \"http: