8, \"end\": 2526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.967418895808315, \"rank\": 0.03367836756036045, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will talk with my people and then make the smartest decision possible to have the best chances to bring some medals back home,\\\" Nadal, who has toyed with ending his glittering career this season because of injuries, said.\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Nadal chases a third Olympic title, 24-time Grand Slam champion Djokovic is yet to bag one in four previous Games.\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2858, \"end\": 2863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7751022731812915e-26, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 2922, \"end\": 2930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.286963451910533e-23, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic has suffered some heart-breaking Olympic disappointments, twice losing in singles semi-finals, with his only medal being a singles bronze from 2008.\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 3131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2974, \"end\": 2982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.286963451910533e-23, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djoko